retweeted_text: The #2018FarmBill is not just for farmers and ranchers, but all Americans. It plays a vital role in ensuring we continue to have access to the safest, most abundant and affordable food supply in the world. This is America's #foodpolicy. https://t.co/pXzE7xn405

full_text: Congrats to @SenPatRoberts & @SenStabenow on passing our strong 2018 #FarmBill conference report in the Senate. This bill is a real shot in the arm to rural America and I urge my colleagues in the House to join me in sending this bill to the president's desk.
